longBusinessSummary: Solnaberg Property AB (publ) operates as a real estate company in Sweden. The company owns, manages, and leases the Solna Bladet 3 property. It operates care rooms, warehouses, garages, and parking lots. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
